name: Skelly Bonez II: Electric Boogaloo
description:
this is a submission for gamedev.js jam 2K22

Join Skelly Bonez in another adventure as they try to retrieve eggs stolen by a pesky band of ghoulish ghosts! Watch out for the electrobudz!

Controls: W, A, S,  D

Objective: place 1 dozen eggs in the basket without dying

music by cyber oats
